-- BioMerieux Cuts 2010 Growth Sales Target; Confirms Operating Margin Goal
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-22T04:53:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/biomerieux-cuts-2010-growth-sales-target-confirms-operating-margin-goal.html

          
          
             BioMerieux SA cut its full-year
sales growth target to 6 percent from a previous forecast of
around 7 percent.  
 The company confirmed its full-year operating margin target
in a statement on Business Wire.  
          
          


  


        